<p>The app is intentionally built to be quick and easy. I designed the app so users wouldnâ€™t have to think about the layout of the boxes themselves. You simply pick the desired layout, and customize the embedded content. At launch, Bento Craft will ship with 3 available layouts: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Mini</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Mega</code>, and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Max</code>.</p>

