<p>The entire idea here is for devs and creators to bring existing assets to Bento Craft. Adding images to Bento Craft couldnâ€™t be easier with the ability to add from your Photos Library, or you can drag and drop images from anywhere right into the app. Bento Craft will even add device frames to your screenshots for you!</p>

<p>Bento Craft also includes an <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">SFSymbol</code> library with configurable colors and gradients to show off your appâ€™s latest capabilities and features. When your creation is complete, you simply tap <strong>Share</strong> and you can send your final image anywhere.</p>

